{
 "name": "RPlog_Rumours_and_old_friends",
 "title": "Rumours and Old Friends",
 "summary": "At a festive gathering on the new training grounds near the Ord Mantell military base, the doctor Lynae Cassius spots the perpetually dour Rasi Cen amid the revelry and makes her way over. After ribbing him about his smoking -- a familiar refrain from years past -- and sharing news of her growing son, the conversation turns serious when Lynae raises troubling rumours. Rasi's controlled blankness returns and he suggests they find somewhere quiet, leading her into the near-empty cafe to talk privately. The reunion of old friends blends warmth and wry humor with the weight of dangerous whispers.",
